'''颞下沟'''（{{lang-en|Inferior temporal sulcus}}）是[[大脑|大脑]][[颞叶|颞叶]]的一个[[脑沟|脑沟]]，位于颞叶下部，向后延伸至[[顶叶|顶叶]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Inferior Temporal Sulcus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/inferior-temporal-sulcus|accessdate=2021-04-10|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Inferior temporal sulcus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/inferior-temporal-sulcus?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-10|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=|publisher=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=BrainInfo|url=http://braininfo.rprc.washington.edu/centraldirectory.aspx?ID=130|accessdate=2021-04-10|work=|publisher=[[华盛顿大学|华盛顿大学]]|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=颞下沟|url=https://www.imaios.com/cn/e-Anatomy/node_322323/2756|accessdate=2021-04-10|work=IMAIOS|language=zh}}</ref>。结构上， 颞下沟分隔了[[颞下回|颞下回]]和[[颞中回|颞中回]]<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />。

命名上，也有将颞下沟称为“颞中沟（middle temporal sulcus）”，在此种命名法中，枕颞沟则被称为“颞下沟”（如右图示）<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Inferior Temporal Area|title=Encyclopedia of Autism Spectrum Disorders|url=https://doi.org/10.1007/978-1-4419-1698-3_564|publisher=Springer|date=2013|location=New York, NY|isbn=978-1-4419-1698-3|pages=1607–1607|doi=10.1007/978-1-4419-1698-3_564|language=en|first=Kevin A.|last=Pelphrey|editor-first=Fred R.|editor-last=Volkmar}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Middle temporal sulcus|url=http://braininfo.org/centraldirectory.aspx?ID=131|access-date=2021-06-03|work=Braininfo|language=en}}</ref>。

== 临床 ==
在治疗部分[[癫痫|癫痫]]患者时，可从颞下沟处进行[[微創手術|微创]]型的{{le|杏仁核海马切除术|Amygdalohippocampectomy}}<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Inferior Temporal Sulcus Approach for Amygdalohippocampectomy Guided by a Laser Beam of Stereotactic Navigator|url=https://doi.org/10.1093/neurosurgery/52.5.1117|last=Miyagi|first=Yasushi|last2=Shima|first2=Fumio|date=2003-05-01|journal=Neurosurgery|issue=5|doi=10.1093/neurosurgery/52.5.1117|volume=52|pages=1117–1124|issn=0148-396X|last3=Ishido|first3=Katsuya|last4=Araki|first4=Takehisa|last5=Taniwaki|first5=Yoshihide|last6=Okamoto|first6=Iku|last7=Kamikaseda|first7=Kazufumi}}</ref>。

